What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Behavioural Biometrics Market?



Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Behavioural Biometrics Market

Behavioural biometrics market will reach at an estimated value of USD 5679.98 million by 2028 and grow at a CAGR of 23.60% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Increase in the number of digital transactions is an essential factor driving the behavioural biometrics market.

Behavioral biometrics solution is generally used for the purpose of identification by examining activities of its users such as signature verification, keystroke dynamics, voice recognition, gesture recognition, and others.

Increase in the development of IoT landscape is a crucial factor accelerating the market growth, also rise in the growth in applications of biometric technology in commercial and government sectors, rise in the sale of smartphones with built-in fingerprint sensors and increase in research and development activities in the market are the major factors among others boosting the behavioural biometrics market. Moreover, rise in the market of cloud-based behavioral biometrics and increase in applications of behavioral biometrics will further create new opportunities for behavioural biometrics market in the forecast period mentioned above.

However, high investment and maintenance costs is the major factor among others restraining the market growth, and will further challenge the behavioural biometrics market in the forecast period mentioned above.

